HEADWORD: Anonymous
<hw>A*non"y*mous</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ without name;
<grk>'an</grk> priv. + <?/, Eol. for <?/ name. See <er>Name</er>.]</ety>
<def>Nameless; of unknown name; also, of unknown or unavowed authorship;
<as>as, an <ex>anonymous</ex> benefactor; an <ex>anonymous</ex> pamphlet
or letter.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

